  "body": "<p>Hope you all enjoyed Plus One week on the <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/\">American Crafts blog</a>. There were so many wonderful projects - love how the same products can be interpreted into many different ways. Here's a little re-cap in case you missed it.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599040159080-Z5UF88I3BK57RKOOYQH6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Monday - <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2014/03/amy-tangerine-plus-one-week.html\">Layouts by Ashley Horton</a><br/>Tuesday - <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2014/03/plus-one-tutorial-by-becki-adams.html\">Mini Album Tutorial by Becki Adams</a> <br/>Wednesday - <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2014/03/plus-one-guest-designer-jen-chesnick.html#comments\">Guest Designer Jen Chesnick</a> <br/>Thursday - <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2014/03/plus-one-cards-by-patricia-roebuck.html\">Cards by Patricia Roebuck</a> <br/>Friday - <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2014/03/plus-one-layout-card-by-elizabeth-gardner.html\">Layout &amp; Card by Elizabeth Gardner</a> </p><p>We're hitting the road in a couple hours for San Diego to teach my first class using Plus One items (available at local stores and online at <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Simon Says Stamp</a> and <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_plus%20one%20amy%20tangerine_/?pp=300&amp;avad=41735_f61d07c5\">Two Peas In A Bucket.)</a> Hope you all have a wonderful weekend!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}